Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小美夜!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有破綻!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,歡樂的夜晚  居然會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,寒假最棒啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,724)}我臥薪嘗膽  經歷了九九八十一難
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.36,0:02:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,724)}終於到達了這片桃源鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我要隨心所欲的休息啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,休長假果然很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去又要變成廢人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:32.64,Comment,,0,0,0,,楓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不能虛度有限的假期
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那就做個預定表吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,早上想睡到飽  晚上也想放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.78,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H777881&\pos(713.667,209.667)}動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.78,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H777881&\pos(774.667,390.667)}睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.78,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H777881&\pos(655.667,568.667)}吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.78,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H777881&\pos(513.667,466.667)}遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.78,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H777881&\pos(519.667,323.667)}吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.78,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H777881&\pos(551.667,184.667)}漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,完…完美!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那到吃晚飯之前  我要一個人打遊戲囉!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,結果還是跟平常一樣啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,蓋亞神在對我說「你庸懶一點吧!」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我的寒假生活方式!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,美波里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,來不來一起打?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這個劇情  難不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喲!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你好!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,來了好多!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要把我帶出門吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不吃你這一套!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽她說  今天是歡樂的睡衣派對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不是小真尋邀請我們的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,睡衣派對…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你究竟在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我把睡衣都帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我也帶過來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是  我也是!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,小真尋是在玩遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真尋尋  給我玩一玩!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  好呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不過這個只能倆個人一起玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐有禮物要給你們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哇!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是你!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好險!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看炸彈!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看我躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然躲開了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  要撞上啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,衝呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,晚飯做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好的!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝款待!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是博士  真會做飯!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了我不是博士啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦  把空盤子拿過來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼…真尋尋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,別忘了懲罰遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你出的主意  卻輸了  真慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是  我是故意輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她們好歹也是客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不過看你還很不甘心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是遊戲  跟別人玩更好玩吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:12.69,Comment,,0,0,0,,以後有機會再玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:13.53,Comment,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.40,Comment,,0,0,0,,我覺得很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:18.20,Comment,,0,0,0,,還想再玩一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那也要看什麼遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,洗完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那要繼續玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太晚了  有點擾民吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,出了一身汗  想先洗個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,確實!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那就按順序來  我最後一個洗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我們分組洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一個一個去洗的話  洗澡水會冷掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好  真尋尋  我來幫你搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,還是讓我來吧  我還能幫你洗頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個先冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小美夜!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那就回歸本心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,「朝×紅」這一對怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,朝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,紅…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  她已經無可救藥了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說  讓我和朝日分勝負嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要來嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那就來猜拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我要出石頭!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下  等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你要負責任  跟我洗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,離這麼近被盯著  實在有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的是長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,性騷擾!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是指那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我小時候  不是給你洗過澡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想起了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你倒是變小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你說誰的責任!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我們洗完了  下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:08:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,小真尋  好可愛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真尋尋好香呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是洗髮精的味道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,行了  快去洗澡吧  朝日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚哇拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.67,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}注 : 在北斗神拳中  阿米巴死前的最後一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,小美夜  也快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可…可三個人一起  也太擠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事  機會難得  就一起洗唄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小美夜先沖身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我們先泡澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這簡直是坐如針氈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不過能近距離觀察她們倆  也挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒跟朝日一起洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你還記得嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我們剛認識的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,朝日來啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫紅葉  請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有丁髷  是武士!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,請多關照  紅葉次郎!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫紅葉!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊  有丁髷真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,要不我也扎一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真是個怪人  既然這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  可愛吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,洗個澡再走?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一起洗沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你不願意嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,倒…倒是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,平常我都和哥哥一起洗的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,以後才會長出來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你指什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然當時還小  可真的很沒禮貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還互相搓澡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓我看看是怎麼搓的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那美夜夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我來給你搓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,別…別給我搓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事  你不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟我經常給哥哥搓背
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,把手舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,輪到胳肢窩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我受到打擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:30.46,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF1ECE5&\3c&HBF9F82&}真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要睡一個房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是睡衣派對  分開睡不會很奇怪嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說  你晚上也想和姐姐一起睡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我為洗澡的事跟你道歉  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,應該沒事  畢竟哥哥你人畜無害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  你把我當什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是被子!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真讓人興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,朝日  你太礙事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你們三個人一起洗澡  不擠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,雖…雖然出了點小意外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,小美夜  你看起來很成熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是喜歡看  不攙和進去的!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,先別管她了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,浴室裡到底發生了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  你們就慢慢玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可別熬太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎麼辦  做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,同問
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,先決定睡哪裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡這裡  畢竟是我的被子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她旁邊歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真狡猾!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這次必須用猜拳來決定!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那我出剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,石頭剪刀布!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,對朝日解讀過度了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老實人必勝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,小真尋你小心點  朝日睡相很差的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧  這可太討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙  居然敢動手!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  這又不是修學旅行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  小真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,吃我這招  消失之魔枕!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都給我消停點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪朝日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,紅葉不也玩得挺高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那接下來就安靜點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那…終於可以開始女生夜談了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,喲  小美夜復活啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,聊天才是睡衣派對的精髓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  雖然不太想參加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  聊點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,戀愛話題吧  還得是戀愛話題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那就讓我先來講吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是恐怖的靈異故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,「妖怪  枕返」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是我親身經歷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我入睡後  深更半夜  在枕頭邊出現了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,枕頭  枕頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,它把別人的枕頭翻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,或者改變人的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這是女生夜談?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是恐怖故事會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋朝日  為什麼要講這麼恐怖的故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:18:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你仔細聽  一點都不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要不要  我聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然這麼害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道她怕這種呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真是個壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我先睡了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  不聊戀愛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,紅葉也有很可愛的地方呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我關燈了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,想上廁所了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  朝日那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,忍到天亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我的被呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,睡相是真不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊  睡得死死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去我會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了  緊急避險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,紅葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是枕返?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺…對不起啊  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,別在意  是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來就交給我  紅葉回去在我的被子裡睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那你睡哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:29.76,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\c&H948284&\3c&H282225&}美波里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  怎麼了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,到時候再說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,半夜喝飲料喝得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊  真拿你沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在怎麼說  也不用替我頂罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事  就別告訴他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那就謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  小朝日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,還在屋裡睡覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,朝日  也很愛賴床的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是枕返!
